title: The Profit Full Season 1 & 2
description:
The Profit Full Season 1 & 2

The Profit is an American reality television show broadcast on CNBC. On each episode Marcus Lemonis,  a successful businessman, offers struggling small businesses capital investment and his expertise in exchange for an ownership stake in the company. The series premiered on July 30, 2013. The second season premiered on February 25, 2014.
